serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">High-Performance Filler</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">1. PP Cotton Core: High elasticity retains shape for 2+ years; non-toxic and dust-mite resistant.</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">2. Airflow Channels: Enhances heat dissipation by 30% vs. standard pillows.</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Durable, Travel-Ready Build</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">1. Double-Layer Quilting: Reinforced edges prevent filler shifting.</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">2. Ultra-Lightweight: 1.1 lbs, folds easily for strollers, car seats, or luggage.</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img data-original="https://cdn.angelhometex.com/cdn/ff/PXpsar5ruzLxVjhYcZPdP5WpAXykEFnyiXA-DtwMmuA/1743380765/public/ueditor/10/upload/image/20250331/1743380765629077.jpg" class="lazy" title="Breathable Cotton Toddler Pillow " alt="Breathable Cotton Toddler Pillow " width="750" height="464" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 750px; height: 464px;" /></span></p><p><br /></p><p><img data-original="https://cdn.angelhometex.com/cdn/ff/uq3Bal9TJX7IqqOSUhtDCS2mLyqA0FIkTZbcpS5V-8I/1743380817/public/ueditor/10/upload/image/20250331/1743380817436578.jpg" class="lazy" title="Breathable Cotton Toddler Pillow " alt="Breathable Cotton Toddler Pillow " width="750" height="750" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 750px; height: 750px;" />  </p><p><br /></p><p><img data-original="https://cdn.angelhometex.com/cdn/ff/Vi-gh5mY_J7AC8qHxqgwxP6Vsy